Package: githubR
Type: Package
Title: This package aims to make it easier to manage Github Repositories by
    using R scripts
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hairizuan
Maintainer: <hairizuanbinnooorazman@gmail.com>
Description: Use this package to power R scripts that can help automate portions
    of Github repository management. If you report off Github, you can use this
    package to deal with extracting that data which you then use familiar R packages
    to get the report you need for your reports.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
